NEW DELHI (AP) - Shugaban Kasar Indiya, Narendra Modi zai halarci wani aikin fara gina wata masallaci na Musulunci a watan gobe a yankin Arewacin Indiya inda wata masallaci ta 16th century ta rushe ta hanyar masu karfi na Musulmi a shekarar 1992, bisa ga kwamitin da ke kula da aikin gina masallacin.
Aikin gudanarwa za a yi ranar 5 ga watan Agusta, wanda masu shirya abin ya ce shi ne mai albarka ga Musulmi amma kuma ya nuna shekara daya tun da Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta Indiya ta kwace ikon kula da ƙasa mai yawan Musulmi, Jammu da Kashmir.
Ba za a iya ɓoye ma'anar ta ba ga masu goyon bayan Modi na Hindu nationalist Bharatiya Janata Party, ko BJP, wanda ya ƙunshi alkawuran da ya shafi ɓata ɓacin rai na Kashmir da kuma gina masallacin Hindu god Ram inda masallacin Mughal-era ya ɓace, wani wuri a birnin Ayodhya a jihar Uttar Pradesh da masu bauta suka yi imani da cewa shi ne asalin haihuwar Ram.
Saboda cutar Korona ta ci gaba da yaduwa a Indiya, wadda ta bayyana ta ɗaya daga cikin ƙananan yawan cututtuka a duniya, za a yada wannan aiki ta hanyar talabijin na jihar, kuma za a ƙayyade yawan masu halarta da masu kallo, bisa ga Vishwa Hindu Parishad, ko Hukumar Hindu ta Duniya, wata ƙungiyar Hindu mai ƙarfi da ta yi aiki tare da BJP.
