Wasu tweets sun kira ga zaman lafiya kuma sun roƙi masu shirya wa su "taimaka mana mu samar da wurare masu tsaro da wurare masu tsaro ga masu bincike."
Bikin nuna bacin ran ya fara a ranar Asabar da misalin karfe 6 na yamma, tare da kungiyoyin kamar "Gidajen Moms," wanda ya yi kama da wata kungiya da aka kafa a Portland, Oregon, lokacin da masu nuna bacin ran suka yi kama da jami'an Amurka da aka aika zuwa wannan birni don tsare wani gidan kotu na tarayya.
Shugaban Ɗonald Trump ya aika sara - sara masu ƙarewa don ƙare bikin nuna goyon baya da aka yi a yau da kullum tun mutuwar George Floyd a Minneapolis a ranar 25 ga Mayu.
Bikin nuna bacin ran Oakland ya fara da zaman lafiya, amma ya ƙare da zama mai tsanani a yammacin dare.
Ƙungiyar da ba ta da izinin yin ta aka sanar da ita da ƙaramin sanda a kusan karfe 11:30 na dare, kuma sanda suka nema mutane su rufe.
Rahotanni sun bayyana cewa wuta ta fara fitowa a gidan kotun Alameda County Superior, kuma an ɗauki matakan tsaro a ƙarƙashin lokaci mai tsawo.
Sojojin sun ce a wani lokaci masu nuna bacin rai suna "bude tagulla da yin maganganu na jinsi ga masu zama."
Hotunan da aka sanya a kan Twitter daga hukumar ta nuna alamun kwano da aka yi a cikin gidan 'yan sanda.
Tsaro mai tsauri a wajen Konsalata ta Amurka a Chengdu, China.
A ranar Lahadi, akwai tsaro mai tsanani a wajen kamfanin kasar Amurka a birnin Chengdu, China, yayin da ma'aikatan Amurka suke shirye-shirye su fita daga wurin.
An ga motocin saukarwa uku sun shigo cikin gidan, yayin da 'yan sanda da 'yan sanda ba su ji ba sun tsaya a dukkan biyun hanyoyin, wadanda aka tsara da katange na metal.
Editan jaridar Global Times ta China ta fitar da tweet cewa U.S. consulate a Chengdu aka ba da izinin rufe a cikin 72 hours ko har zuwa 10 a.m. (0200GMT) Litinin, 27 ga Yuli.
China ta zargi cewa wasu ma'aikata a consulate na Chengdu suna "aikata ayyuka ba daidai da haɗin kansu ba".
Ba tare da bayyana kowane ƙarin bayani ba , mai magana da yawun Hukumar Shige-da-Fice ta Sin , Wang Wenbin ya ce wannan aikin ya shiga tsakanin al'amuran Sin kuma ya cutar da dangantakar tsaro.
An sanya umarnin ƙasashen Sin da ya ce ya ƙare kantin sashen Chengdu a ranar Alhamis a matsayin dakatarwa ga umarnin ƙasashen Amurka da ya ce ya ƙare kantin sashen Sin a Houston, Texas.
Washington ya umurci China ta rufe ofishin Houston "don kare haƙƙin mallaka na zamani da bayanai na yan'Amerika."
Da fara aiki na rufe kantin kasar Sin a Houston a Juma'a, an gani wani ɗan takarar Amurka da ya bayyana yana shigowa cikin wannan wurin ta hanyar wata baya.
Wang ya ce Alhamis cewa ya yi wa dokoki na tsakanin ƙasashe da kuma dokoki na biyu kuskure, kuma China za ta amsa ba tare da bayyana yadda ba.
