Juma'a da dare, Ma'aikatar Ƙasar Amurka ta fitar da wata sanarwa cewa tawagar zaman lafiya ta ta, Zalmay Khalilzad, ta sake yin tafiya a cikin yankin don fara wannan tattaunawa da aka sake kawar da ita da yawa, saboda dai dukkanin bangarorin suna yin kokarin gudanar da wani shirin sakin jama'a.
Wata ƙungiya da Amurka ta goyi bayan ta buƙaci gwamnatin Afghan ta saki 5,000 mambobin Taliban, kuma Taliban su saki 1,000 ma'aikatan gwamnati da na soja a matsayin wani nuni na alheri kafin tattaunawa.
Har yanzu gwamnatin ta ki sakin 'yan Taliban da yawa da take kira masu laifi muhimmanci, kuma ta bayar da zaɓuɓɓuka don sakin su.
Taliban sun ki.
An karɓi sanarwar ƙungiyar ƙasa ta Amurka, an ce, "Ƙungiyoyin sun fi kusa da fara tattaunawa tsakanin ƙasashen Afaganistan, wanda shine mataki muhimmin gaba wajen ƙarewa yakin shekaru 40 da Afaganistan ya sha."
Koda yake an yi nasarar yin musayar marasa lafiya mai yawa, amma an buƙaci a yi karin aiki don gama magance matsalar.
Ɗan sanda na siyasa na Taliban a ranar Litinin da ta gabata ya ce suna shirye su yi magana da jagororin siyasa na Kabul bayan sallah na Eid al-Adha a ƙarshen wannan watan, in an gama da saki mutane daga hannunsu.
Wani abu mai tsanani ga Pakistan shi ne cewa a Afghanistan akwai 'yan ta'adda, musamman waɗanda suke da alaƙa da TTP ko Jamaat-ul-Ahrar ko Lashkar-e-Islam, kuma waɗanda suke da Baluchistan Liberation Army, wanda ya ɗauki alhakin yunkurin da suka yi a wannan wata a yankin Sindh ta Kudu da kuma yankin Baluchistan ta Kudu.
Wataƙila ɗaliban sojojin Pakistan sun mutu a watan wannan a yankin Kudancin Baluchistan yayin yakin da suka yi da masu yaki.
TTP ta ɗauki alhakin wani daga cikin mafi munin matafiyar da aka yi a Pakistan a shekarar 2014, lokacin da aka yi matafiyar a makarantar sojojin Pakistan, inda aka kashe 140.
Da yawa daga cikinsu suna ɗalibai , kuma wasu suna da shekaru huɗu ko biyar.
Rahoton ya ce, "An kiyasta cewa, a ƙasar Afghanistan, yawan jami'an tsaron ƙasashen waje na Pakistan da suke haifar da wahala ga biyu ƙasashe, ya kai tsakanin 6,000 zuwa 6,500, mafi yawan su suna da alhakin TTP."
Bankin ƙasar Birtaniya mafi girma HSBC ta musanta cewa ta "sanya hanyar tsoro" ga Huawei a bincike da ake yi a Amurka - RT Business News
Bankin kasashen waje HSBC da ke ƙasar London ya yi amfani da sada zumunta don ce ba kamar yadda jaridun Sin suka ce ba, "suna ƙirƙirar bayanai" a kan Huawei, wanda ya haifar da ɗaukar hankali ga mataimakin shugaban kuɗi na kamfanin a Kanada.
A cikin wani post da ba a samu a yanzu a kan WeChat, mai bashi ya ce ayyukansa ba su tashi US bincike game da mafi girma samarwa na tsarin wayar tarho a duniya, saboda binciken Huawei na zargin ta ta karya dokar US akan Iran ya fara kafin shiga bankin a shekarar 2016.
Bankin HSBC bai yi wata ƙarancin jin ƙai ga Huawei ba, kuma bai "tsara" Huawei ba, bankin ya ce ranar Asabar, yana ƙara da cewa bai taba ƙaryata kowane fa'ida game da abokan ciniki nasa ba.
A cikin amsar buƙatun DOJ na Amurka [Hukumar Adalci ta Amurka] na bayanai, HSBC Group ya bayar da fa'idodin gaskiya.
HSBC ba ta "tsara" shaida ko "ƙare" bayanai ba.
Kuma a kan rt.com Aikin UK na ɓoye Huawei daga tsarin 5G ya nuna cewa Amurka ta yanke shawarar siyasa ta waje ta Birtaniya - George Galloway zuwa Boom Bust.
Post din an rufe shi a kan wannan platform tare da wata rubutu cewa "yana ƙoƙarin ƙoƙarin kaɗa dokoki" kuma ba shi samuwa yanzu ba.
Wannan bayani ya zo nan da nan bayan da jaridun da suka haɗa da na ƙasa suka zargi HSBC da "haduwa" da Birnin Washington don yin wani tsari ga Huawei.
Kamfanin ya zama a cikin ƙaramin rikici na siyasa tsawon shekaru ɗaya da rabi tun da aka kama Mataimakin Shugaban Huawei Meng Wanzhou a watan Disamba 2018 a Kanada a kan umarnin daga Amurka.
Meng ta fuskanci tuhuma na yaudara saboda an zargi ta da amfani da kamfanin ƙaramin kamfanin don ta karya dokoki game da Iran, kuma an zargi ta da yin karya ga bankuna game da alaka tsakanin Huawei da kamfanin Iran Skycom.
Bayan bayanai da Global Times ya bayar, HSBC ya san cikakken alaka da kamfanin Sin da Skycom.
An ruwaito cewa banki ya zaɓi "hadawa" da gwamnatin Amurka don tsallake mafi girma mai hukunci a shekarar 2012, lokacin da banki ya yi amfani da laundare kudi da laifuffuka na yankin, ciki har da kulle kan Iran.
An umarci a lokacin a biya kusan dala biliyan 1.9 don gudanar da hukunci da kuma hana kowane irin laifin da ya shafi.
Bayanai sun nuna cewa HSBC ta fahimci wannan alaka amma ta nufin siyar da sakonnin sirri na abokan ciniki ga ƙasar Amurka don ganin gwamnatin Amurka ta ƙi yin hukunci a kanta a kan laifin da ta aikata a cikin 2012 Deferred Prosecution Agreement, kamar yadda jaridar ta bayyana a cikin wata makala ta kan wannan batu.
A cikin wani alamar da aka tsare, jaridar da Beijing take kula da ita ta ƙara cewa, idan an tabbatar da cewa wannan kamfanin kuɗi ya aikata "hadaka," zai iya fuskantar "hukunci mai tsanani" a ƙasar Sin, wata daga cikin manyan kasuwannin da HSBC ke aiki a ciki.
Ba ƙarshen farko ba ne bankin da ya fi sani ya samu kurakurai a cikin makonni masu zuwa.
A watan da ya gabata, HSBC an yi musu korafi saboda ta goyon bayan dokar tsaron jama'a ta sabuwar Hong Kong, wadda ita ce birnin da suka fara aikinsu kuma wanda ya kasance mai bashi fiye da rabin kudinsu.
Banki ya fuskanci kalamai daga dukkan bangarorin - daga yammacin, tare da US Secretary of State Mike Pompeo yana kiran goyon bayan da "corporate kowtow," da kuma gabashin, tare da bangaren Sin ya ce goyon bayansa ya yi "belated".
