Aljeriya: Mutuwar Mahmoud Guemama - Aljeriya Ta Rasa Ɗan Ƙasa, Wanda Ya Yi Alƙawarin Ɗaukaka, In Ji Shugaban Tebboune.
Aljir - Shugaban Rasha, Abdelmadjid Tebboune, ya aika sakon ta'aziyya ga 'yan majalisar Mutanen Kasa (APN), Mujahed Mahmoud Guemama, wanda ya rasu Alhamis, inda ya ce Aljeriya "ta rasa jinin ƙasƙanin da ya yi wa al'ummar da kuma ƙasar sa aiki".
A yau Algeria ta rasa Mujahed Mahmoud Guemama, wani ƙwararren mutum da ya yi aiki tare da ƙwararrun 'yan uwa da ƙasa, wanda bai taba yin wani sauyi ba kuma ƙarfin sa ya kasance mai ƙarfi daga lokacin da ya fara yin aiki tare da ƙwararrun 'yan uwa masu yaki har zuwa lokacin da ya rasu a yau wannan rana mai tsanani inda muka iya kawo mana kawai ga yabo da Allah ya yi," Shugaban Tebboune ya rubuta a sakonin ta'aziyyarsa.
"Mahmoud Guemama, Allah ya yi masa rahama, ya kasance daga cikin wata ƙarni mai ƙarfi da masu yin sadaukarwa wa ƙasarsu," in ji Shugaban ƙasa.
Wanda ya rasu ya yi wa ƙasƙantar Aljeriya daga cin zarafin kolonialism ɗin ƙasƙanci, ta shiga ƙungiyar ƙasƙanci a shekarar 1960 a yankin Tahart na shekara ta ƙasar ta VI.
Shugaban ɓarayi ya yi sanadiyyar ƙarfi da kuma alƙawarin da ya yi na tabbatar da hoton ƙasar Aljeriya mai ci gaba da ƙungiyarci, in ji Shugaban Tebboune.
A ƙasan ƙarƙashin ƙasa, Mahmoud Guemama wanda ya rasu ya samu kyautar suna a matsayin wanda ya yi wa shawara, yana shiga tsakanin 'yan'uwa a cikin ƙasar nan idan wuta na rashin jituwa ta fara ɗauka," shugaban ya ƙara a cikin saƙoninsa.
"Dukkan wadannan siffofi da kima sun samar da late Mahmoud Guemama ƙarfin ƙauna da aminci daga mutanen Tamanrasset wadanda suka zaba shi don su ɗauki nauyin su a Majalisar Mutane ta Kasa (APN) a cikin yanayi da yawa, lokacin da ya zama sakataren kasashen waje da kuma ɗan kare muhimman abubuwan yankin da burin mutanensa, har ma da wakilin da ya yi magana a kai a gare dukkan aljiran," in ji shugaban kasa.
Ba za a iya yin komai ba don yin nasiha ga mujahed Mahmoud Guemama, Allah ya yi masa rahama.
Ya bar mu yau a lokacin da Aljeriya take buƙata shi," in ji shugaban.
Ina addu'a ga Ubangiji Mai Girma ya rufe mai rasuwa da RahamarSa Mai Tsarki, ya karɓe shi cikin ƙasarsa mai ƙarfi tare da shuhadar da masu tsarki.
Ina kuma addu'a ga Allah ya ba iyalinsa da waɗanda ya ƙauna ƙarfin hankali da rahama ... babu ƙarfi ko iko sai daga Allah," Shugaban Jamhuriyar ya ƙare.
Bikin Yaki a Seattle: Wuta da Man Tsami a Yayin Da Dubban Mutane Suka Tafi Ta Jirgin Kasa Ta Yankin Birnin
SEATTLE - Bayan mako-mako na karuwar tuhuma tsakanin masu yin zanga-zangar da hukumomin tarayya a Portland, Ore., jama'a da suka kai dubu biyu sun tashi a Seattle a Asabar, suka yi tafiya a cikin tituna kuma suka yi kalubale da sojojin.
Jami'an 'yan sanda uku sun ji rauni, ciki har da wanda aka ajiye a asibiti da rauni a jikinsa da aka yi ta amfani da makamai, kuma har zuwa yamma, an kama 16 masu yin zanga-zangar, in ji jami'an 'yan sanda.
Suna ɗaukar alamomi kamar "Feds Go Home" da kuma kiran kiran "Ba adalci ba zaman lafiya," masu bai wa jama'a kararraka sun tsaya a wurin wani gidan yari na masu zuwa da suka watsa gidajen a can da wuta.
Wasu ƙofofi na gidajen da ke kusa sun rushe.
Ɗan sanda sun yi kallon jama'a a yankin Capitol Hill, suna aiwatar da makamai na haske da mai tsami kafin su fara ɗaukar mutane cikin hannu.
Bipasha Mukherjee, da shekara 52, daga Kirkland, Wash., ta ce ta yi tserewa a tituna tun daga watan Mayu, kuma ta ce ta yi tsoro sosai da ganin hanyoyin da sojojin suka yi da suka nuna karfi.
"Wannan ba ƙasar da na shiga ba ce," in ji Ms. Mukherjee, wadda ta zo daga Indiya fiye da shekaru 30 da suka wuce.
Yana da kamar muna cikin sauri muna zama ƙasa mai ƙungiyar ƙasashen fashi da ƙasa mai tsaro.
