Jami'an 'yan sanda sun ce sun kama wani mai shekaru 37 a ranar Lahadi saboda laifin kashe wani ɗansa, wanda aka samu an ajiye shi a wata ƙauyen da ba ta da alaka da wani a jihar Uttar Pradesh ta Greater Noida da wata ɗaya da suka wuce.
Wataƙila, yayin da aka yi magana da ƙaramin ƙawayen, ya bayyana wa 'yan sanda cewa ya yi fushi da sha'awar ƙawayensa na yin sha'awar mata masu zama a ƙungiyar ƙawayen, wanda ya sa ya aikata laifi, kamar yadda aka bayyana daga ofishin.
Jikin Bhisham Singh, wani ɗan gari ne daga Bisrakh a Greater Noida, an samo shi a kusa da tsami a wata ɓangare mai ɓacewa kusan wata ɗaya da suka wuce.
Wata ƙungiyar ƙwadago ta ce an gano cewa jikin ya ƙunshi alamun ƙarfe da aka yi, kuma an shigar da rahoton a sashen ƙwadago na Bisrakh, kuma an fara bincike.
A cikin binciken, shaidar ta haifar da 'yan sanda zuwa ga wanda ya rasu, ya ƙare, ya ƙare Deepak, kuma an tambayesa. Lallai Deepak ya yi waɗannan bayanin ya ƙashe ɗan uwansa. Ya gaya wa 'yan sanda cewa Bhisham zai yi amfani da giya sosai, ya yi rikici a gida, kuma ya yi laifi da mata masu iyali, saboda haka ya yanke shawarar ya ƙashe ɗan uwansa, ya ce shi mai magana.
