Bethe Correia, mai ƙarfi ɗaya daga Brazil, ita ce mai shekaru a cikin UFC amma ta yi kuskure na amfani da ta ɓace daga mataimakiyar ta Pannie Kianzad, kuma ta yi kuskure ta yi tunanin cewa rana ta ƙare a yayin taron su a Fight Island, kuma ta sami taga a sakamakon haka.
A ƙarshe na farkon stanza na musayar su a kan katin ƙasa a Abu Dhabi, Correia mai shekaru 37 ya yi kuskure ya ƙara da 10-second warning kamar ƙarshe na rana, ya ƙara da hannu kafin ya juya baya ga Kianzad ya tafi gida zuwa ƙofar sa.
Ɗan wasan ƙasar Sweden ya yi amfani da sauri ba tare da jinkirtawa ba, ya yi taga wa mai karewa da hannu dama kafin ya bi ta da wani tashin hankali na kama Correia a kusurwar ƙarfe.
A cikin wani lokaci mai tsawo da ya bayyana a matsayin wani abu mai tsanani, sai Brazilian ya dakatar da wannan tsananin kuma ya dawo da karfin kansa don hana Kianzad kafin kammala karbar rana.
Abin da ya faru a nan? Oh Allah, an ji kungiyar karin bayani a kan ESPN+ suna yin magana.
Wannan kawai ɗaya daga cikin dare mai cike da tashin hankali ga tsohon takarar mai suna Correia, wacce ta fadi a zaben jama'a wanda ya zama ta ta farko a cikin tafiyoyinta huɗu a cikin ɗakin kwandon, kuma ya bar ta da rikodin 11-5, tare da ɗaya daga cikin kulawa.
Ga Kianzad mai haifuwa daga Iran, wanda ya shekara 28, wannan ya zama nasara ta biyu a jere bayan nasararta a kan Jessica-Rose Clark a UFC Fight Night a Moscow a watan Nuwamba.
Kianzad yanzu 13-5 baki ɗaya kuma 2-1 a cikin UFC, yayin da mace da aka sani da 'Banzai' take nufin canza jerin 135lbs.
A ranar da ta wuce, Robert Whittaker na Australia ya yi nasara a kan Darren Till na Birtaniya a cikin babban taron tsakiya, yayin da mai karɓar kasar Rasha, Khamzat Chimaev, ya yi tarihi ta yin nasara a kan biyu a cikin 10 kwanaki a kan Ƙasar Kaka, wanda ya zama mafi sauri tsakanin nasarori a cikin UFC na zamani.
