Idan Emiliano Martinez ba ya yi nasarar bada taimako akan backheel na Danny Welbeck a cikin 16 da mintuna, bayan da abokin tafiyarsa ya shiga cikin kwallon don ƙara Watford a cikin biyu na tsaro, to lalle akwai dukkan yiwuwar su kammala komawa mai shekaru.
A ƙarshe sun kasa, kuma ma'aikacin su na kula da su, Hayden Mullins, zai iya tunawa cewa ba zai samu wannan aikin mafi ƙarancin godiya ba idan tawagar ta nuna aikin da ya dace da gabannin.
A cikin shekara bai yi kyau ba, amma kuma ma ba aikin da suke yi bai yi kyau ba.
Ɗaya kamfani mai ƙarancin kuɗi ba zai ƙone ƙasar ba, amma kuma babban gini da Pozzo ɗan'uwa suka ɗora ba ya tabbatar da cewa za su sake tashi daga matakin na biyu ba.
Babu shakka cewa yanayin Watford na canza masu shugabancin yana da wahala ya ƙare.
Na ɗaya bayan ɗaya - a cikin mafi ƙarancin ma'ana - za su yi zaben na ɗaya goma sha biyar a cikin shekaru huɗu, kuma babu abin da ƙaramin sallama zai iya sauya a cikin hawa mai tsabta.
Troy Deeney ya yi kokarin hana ƙetare daga ƙungiyar, kuma ya samu nasara a Emirates inda ya samu lambar gogewa.
Wasu 'yan wasan za su tafi, Ismaïla Sarr ya nuna nan cewa ba zai yi yiwuwa ya yi wasa da kwallon kafa na Championship a Satumba ba, kuma wani hannu mai tsayi ya zama abin dogaro.
Ba wani abu mai tsawo game da fare mai karuwa ko raguwa a wani taron da Mikel Arteta ya bayyana kamar "wani ɗan wasan kwando," koda kuwa ya yi daidai da kyautar kallo.
Arteta ya ce bayan haka, 'yan gaba na Watford suna "yin karya," duk da cewa ya dakatar da sauri cewa wannan shine ɗan wasan kwaikwayo don "yin wasa, zama a gaba."
Sun tabbata suna buƙatar: kowane shawara cewa wani motsi zai iya isa ga ƙarshe an yi sauri ya ƙare kuma suna iya tambayar yadda abubuwa za su faru idan ba su da buƙatar yin kokarin kama.
