Ted Cruz ya ce manufofin Pelosi suna "shoveling kudi akan matsalar kuma suna rufe Amurka".
Sanata Ted Cruz na Jam'iyyar Jamhuriyar Tarayya ta Texas ya zargi Gwamnan Majalisar Wakilai Nancy Pelosi da Jam'iyyar Dimokuradiyya ta Majalisar Wakilai da neman aiwatar da kayan aiki na magance cutar coronavirus wanda ya kunshi "sadaukar da kudi akan matsalar kuma kashe Amurka" yayin da huldodin kan matakin gaba ke ci gaba.
A cikin wata tattaunawa da "Fuskanci Al'umma" a ranar Lahadi, Cruz ya ce kasar ta fuskanci biyu matsaloli a wurare guda: cutar da ta addabi duniya wadda ta kashe rayukan mutane fiye da 600,000 a duniya baki ɗaya, da kuma "tsawon ƙalubale na tattalin arziki" a Amurka.
Amma Cruz ya ce Pelosi, wacce ta bayyana a "Fuskanci Al'umma" kafin senatocin, "ba ta ƙunshi wani daga cikin waɗannan ba".
"Manufofinta ita ce ta yi ƙoƙarin ƙara kuɗi akan matsalar kuma ta ƙare Amurka," in ji Jam'iyyar Ɗaya ta Texas.
Kuma musamman, ka duba $3 trillion kudin da take kokarin sauya, kawai yana ɗaukar kudi zuwa abokaninta ba tare da gano matsalar ba. Manufarmu ya kamata ta yi cewa Amurka suna so su dawo aiki. Suna so su iya bayar da abinci ga iyalinsu.
'Yan majalisar dattawa na jam'iyyar ƙwaryar ƙwabo da gidan White House sun yi kwanan nan ta yin magana kan sharuddan na tsarin magance cutar coronavirus na hudu, wanda suka sa ran zai kasance da kudin dala biliyan ɗaya.
A cikin kwanakin jumma'a, shugaban ma'aikatar gidan White House Mark Meadows da ma'aikatar kudin Amurka Steven Mnuchin suka koma Capitol Hill don yin hira da ma'aikatan majalisar dattawa, kuma Mnuchin ya gaya wa Fox News a cikin wata tattaunawa da ta gudana a ranar Lahadi cewa bayanai za a bayyana su ne ta hanyar shugaban majalisar dattawa Mitch McConnell a ranar Litinin.
Matsalar da take da muhimmanci ga masu siyar da dokoki - kuma wani batu na rashin jituwa tsakanin Jam'iyyar Jamhuriyar Dimokuradiyya da Jam'iyyar Jamhuriyar Republikanci - shine ƙarewar ƙarin albashi na aiki, wanda ya fara ɓace a wannan Asabar.
Yayin da Jam'iyyar Dimokuraɗiyya take so ta ci gaba da kara wa albashi $600 a cikin kayan aikin na coronavirus na zamani na hudu, Jam'iyyar Ɗaya ta ƙirƙiri kuɗin ya ƙare kuma ta yi ƙoƙarin nuna cewa wasu Amurka suna samun albashi mafi yawa daga aikin matafiyi fiye da yadda suka samu daga aikin aiki.
Cruz ya ce fiye da ƙaramin ɗan Amurka da suke samun sakamakon karuwar albashi suna samun kudin da yawa fiye da lokacin da suke aiki, kuma ya ce ya tattauna da masu gidajen yarinya a Texas wadanda suke fama da matsalar sake dawo da ma'aikata.
Ya ce, "Lalle ba za su dawo ba saboda gwamnatin tarayya ta biya musu, a wasu yanayi, dubban kudin don su zauna gida."
Cruz ya ce Majalisar Dattawa ta kamata ta yi kokarin ƙirƙirar wani shiri na sake samun karfi wanda zai sa ya sauƙi ga Amurka su dawo aiki ta hanyar sauya sutura da dokoki a kan kamfanonin yar-gaje: "babu wani abu da zai sa a yi amfani da triliyoyin daloli, wani shiri na sake samun karfi zai tsaya sutura na albashin aiki, wanda zai ba duk wanda ke aiki a Amurka ƙarin albashin aiki. Wannan yana da mahimmanci wajen sa mutane su dawo aiki," ya ce.
Shugaban Trump ya bukaci a watan da ya gabata cewa akwatin gaggawa na gaba ya ƙunshi ƙaramin kudin shiga, amma Mnuchin ya ce ba zai ƙunshi wannan a cikin dokar ba, saboda takardar shawarar ta samu karɓuwa mai ƙarfi daga masu jam'iyyar Republican.
Malamin Trump ya yarda cewa kuɗin ƙarfe zai ƙare daga sakon da zai biyo bayan sa amma ya yi niyyar yin la'akari da laifin ga Jam'iyyar Dimokuradiyya.
Cruz, wanda ya yi kalubale ga kudin ɗakunan da za a yi a makon jiya, ya ce Laraba bai yarda da matakin da 'yan majalisar dokokin sa suka dauka ba.
Amma ya kuma yi wa wannan kudin dala biliyan 3 da aka ƙarɓa da ƙwaryar jam'iyyar Dimokuraɗiyya a watan Mayu karɓa, kuma ya zargi 'yan takararsa da nufin yin wani mataki wanda zai cutar da shugaban kafin zaben watan Nuwamba.
"Gaba ɗaya abin da Jam'iyyar Dimokradiyya take nufi shi ne a kawar da Donald Trump, kuma sun yanke shawarar cewa hanyar da za su kawar da shi ita ce a rufe duk kamfanoni a Amurka, da kuma rufe duk makarantu a Amurka," ya ce.
Ka sani , Nancy Pelosi ta yi magana game da maza da mata masu aiki. Abinda take nufi shi ne kare maza da mata masu aiki daga aiki.
Rahul Gandhi Ya Tafi Wa Mutane Kan Matsalar Rajasthan
Rahula Gandhi na Majalisar Wakilai ya aika wata bidiyo yau don tada hankali ga mutane a kan jam'iyyar BJP a kan abubuwan da suka faru a Jihar Rajasthan.
Yana amfani da hashtag #SpeakUpForDemocracy, Hindia ya yi kira ga mutane su "Yi haɗin kai kuma kada muryar mu don dimokuradiyya."
Majalisar Dattawa ta shirya yin bikin nuna bacin rai a kasar nan a ranar Litinin saboda halin da ake ciki a Jihar Rajasthan, inda Gwamnatin Ashok Gehlot take fuskantar matsala wajen ci gaba da rayuwa.
Yayin da jam'iyyar ta ce za a yi bikin bana a waje na Rashtrapati Bhavan, gidajen gwamnatin shugaban Ram Nath Kovind.
A cikin bidiyon, Majalisar Dattawa ta zargi BJP da "Ripping up kundin tsarin mulki da kawar da dimokuradiyya" yayin da kasar gaba ɗaya take yaki da cutar Korona.
Jam'iyyar Kongo ta ce ta yi haka a Jihar Madhya Pradesh.
"Mun buƙaci a yi wani zaman taro da za a yi nan da nan wanda ya shafi hakkarmu na kundin tsarin mulki," jam'iyyar ta ce a cikin bidiyon.
Gwamnan Rajasthan Kalraj Mishra ya ki yarda da wata shawara ta fara taron majalisar.
Wata biyu an aike ta yau wadda ya ce yana bin diddigin ta.
Gwamnatin Mr Gehlot ta shiga cikas bayan da ma'aikacinsa Sachin Pilot ya zama mai ƙalubale tare da ɗayan ɗakunan MLAs da suka taimaka masa.
Jam'iyyar ba ta iya ƙi ƙoƙarin ƙwace izinin masu ƙarya doka don ƙare ƙimar yawanci a cikin majalisar.
Malamin Jirgin Saman -- wanda aka yanke masa dukkanin matsayoyinsa a cikin jam'iyya da gwamnati -- an ba shi taimako na wani lokaci daga cin zarafin da Rajasthan High Court ta yi, inda ta yanke shawarar cewa Babban Magatakarda ba zai iya yin wani aiki har sai an yanke shawarar kan tambayar kundin tsarin da ya shafi ikoninsa.
Wannan tambaya za a ɗauka gobe ta gaban Kotun Shugaban Kasa, wanda zai yanke shawarar ko Kotun zai iya shiga tsakanin matakan Shugaban Majalis.
Majalisar Dattawa ta kasance ɗaya kawai a bayan ƙimar yawan jama'a a cikin ƙungiyar da ke da ɗari biyu da dubu.
Team Pilot ya ce ya samu goyon bayan 30 MLAs, amma har yanzu, bayanai sun nuna kawai 19.
BJP ta samu 72, kuma tare da abokan aiki da masu yin kai tsaye, an kai ta 97.
Idan kotu ya yanke hukunci a ƙ favor ɗin Mr Pilot, Majalisar Dattawa za ta iya rasa na biyu daga cikin uku da ta kafa a jihohin da ke cikin ƙasashen gabas bayan zaben majalisar 2018.
A watan Maris, ya rasa gwamnatin Kamal Nath-led a Madhya Pradesh bayan Jyotiraditya Scindia ya shiga BJP tare da 22 daga cikin MLAs nasa.
'Yan sanda na Kenya suna cikin hannu bayan wani rauni mai tsanani a Garissa.
Biyu daga cikin 'yan sanda a Kenya suna garkuwa da laifin rufe-rufen da ya haifar da mutuwar biyu.
An yi raunuka a sashin Soko Ng'ombe a yankin Garissa ta gabas a Asabar, lokacin da ake yin bikin nuna bacin rai game da tsare wani mutum da aka zargi da kashe mutane.
An sanya sunan biyu masu rauni a matsayin Aden Abdi Madobe da Muhiyadin Adow Shibin.
Kwamitin tsaro na ƙasa na Kenya ya fara bincike kan rikicin da aka yi.
Za ta ƙunshi binciken hukunci na makamai na 'yan sanda.
MP Aden Duale na Garissa ya kira mutuwa "mai laifi" kuma ya yi wa "tsaro taƙawa" karɓa a cikin wata sanarwa da aka aika a shafin Facebook.
Masu neman zabe sun yi tashin hankali game da tsaro a lokacin cutar Korona.
Cikin ƙididdigar Amnesty International, 'yan sanda na Kenya sun kashe mutane 21 tun daga Maris saboda rashin biyan buƙatun hana yaduwar cutar coronavirus, kamar yadda ake buƙatar yin sallar yamma da yin rufe baki.
