Manema labarai sun ce wannan taron na wannan shekara ya samu ƙarin ƙarfi saboda fushi da aka yi game da kwace-kwace da 'yan sanda suka yi a lokacin da aka yi tsaron Covid-19.
Shivraj Singh Chouhan ya yi Positive akan gwajin Covid.
Shugaban Ƙasar Madhya Pradesh, Shivraj Singh Chouhan, wanda ya tabbatar da ya yi gwajin jiki da COVID-19 a Asabar, ya tweet a ranar Lahadi da safe cewa yana "lafiya" kuma ya yi godiya ga masu aikin farko a yakin da ake yi da cutar coronavirus.
Ministan Shugaban kuma ya sake jaddada waɗannan alƙawari daga jiya, lokacin da ya kira mutane su bi umarnin, kamar yadda suka shafi tsakanin jama'a da amfani da masu fuska.
Ni lafiya, abokaina.  Sadaukarwa da masu yaki da cutar Korona suka yi, wadanda suka yi wa kansu sadaukarwa ba tare da neman komai ba, ya kamata a yaba.  Ina yabawa duk masu yaki da cutar Korona a jihar, in ji Shugaban Chouhan daga Asibitin Chirayu da ya shiga jiya a Bhopal.
Ka tsaya biyu mita daga juna, ka tsabtace hannunka da yawa, kuma ka sanya masu fuska - waɗannan su ne mafi girma makamai da muke da su don kawar da cutar Korona. Ina neman alfahari ga dukkan mutane - amfani da waɗannan makamai don kanka da waɗanda kake so," ya ce.
Ku dukkanin ku ku yi hankali , ku kasance lafiya da lafiya. Wannan shine abin da nake addu'a wa Allah, Mr Chouhan ya kara da cewa.
Ranar Asabar Malam Chouhan ya yi sakon a Twitter cewa ya yi gwajin da ya nuna cewa ya kamu da cutar, kuma ya yi waɗannan kira da cewa "kawai ɗan ɗan kuskure ne zai kawo cutar Korona."
Yau da safe, Mr Chouhan ya tweet cewa duk da cewa akwai tashin hankali na cutar, babu buƙatar tsoro, kuma ya kira wa waɗanda suka nuna alamu su yi nazarin su.
"Idan ka kamu da cutar, ba dole ba ne ka tsorata. Kada ka ɓoye alamun cutar ba, sai ka fada wa likitoci nan da nan, don a fara magani. Magani da lokaci zai sa ka lafiya," ya ce.
