Ministan cikin gida na Tunisia ya zaba sabon shugaban karamar hukuma, don samar da gwamnati a cikin wata ɗaya.
Ofishin shugaban ƙasa ya ce, ministan gidajen ƙasar Tunisiya, Hichem Mechichi, an nada shi don ƙirƙirar gwamnatin gaba, a cikin tashin hankali tsakanin jam'iyyun goma na ƙasar Afirka ta Arewa.
Wannan shari'a mai shekaru 46 ya ci gaba da Elyes Fakhfakh, wanda ya isa ya bar matsayin shugaban kasa a wannan wata.
Amma Mechichi ba shi ne ɗayan sunayen da jam'iyyun siyasa suka nuna wa shugaban kasa Kais Saied ba.
A cikin wata sanarwa da aka bayar bayan sanarwar Asabar, Mechichi ya ce zai "aiki don samar da gwamnati wadda za ta cika burin dukkan Tunisiyawa."
Tunisia ta samu yabo a matsayin misali mai ban mamaki na ci gaba da zaman lafiya bayan ƙarƙashin ƙasa da aka yi a yankin Arab Spring da aka fara ta hanyar ƙaddamar da ta 2011.
Amma shugabannin sun yi kokarin cimma burin jama'ar Tunisiya da kuma tattalin arziki da ya riga ya yi karancin ƙarfi saboda rufe iyakokin ƙasar saboda cutar COVID-19.
Cutar ta kashe kusan mutane 50 da suka yi yawan fiye da 1400 a Tunisiya.
A ƙarƙashin mulkin da ya fita, Mechichi ya zama ministan cikin gida, kuma ya zama mai shawara ga Shugaban Saied, inda ya yi aiki da al'amuran shari'a.
Ya taba zama shugaban ma'aikata a Ma'aikatar Harkokin Jirgin Kasa, kuma ya yi aiki a Ma'aikatar Harkokin Al'umma.
Yau ya ɗauki wata ɗaya don samar da gwamnati , wadda za ta yi ficewa a zaben majalisar dokokin kuma za ta buƙaci ƙaramiya mai ƙarfi don cimma nasara.
Idan ba haka ba, majalisar dokokin za a ɓace ta, kuma za a gudanar da zaɓe - zaɓe sabuwa cikin watanni uku.
A zaben da aka yi a watan Oktoba, jam'iyyar Ennahdha ta samu nasara amma ta ƙare kusanci ƙaramiya, sannan ta amince ta shiga cikin gwamnatin hadin kai.
Reshen Fakhfakh a ranar 15 ga watan Yuli, bayan ƙananan watanni shida a ofishin, ya haifar da matsala ta siyasa saboda yadda ƙasar take fuskantar sauyin tattalin arziki na cutar pandemiyar.
Aikin ƙarewa ya ƙara tsananta rikici tsakanin Ennahdha da Fakhfakh game da zargin rashin daidaito.
Kamar yadda zaben majalisar dokoki ya faru a watan Oktoba, haɗuwar tsakanin shugaban da ya fita mai shekaru 47 da kuma Ennahdha ta yi kururuwa.
Fakhfakh ya sauka a ranar da jam'iyyar ta aika da motar kalamai ba tare da gaskiya ba a kansa.
Ennahdha ya fara nuna wani ɗan kasuwa a matsayin shugaban kasa, amma bai samu goyon bayan majalisar dokokin, wanda ya sa shugaban ya sanya mai girma ministan kudi Fakhfakh a matsayin shugaban kasa.
Bayan ganin cewa za a yi zaben sabon, Ennahdha ƙarshe ta amince ta shiga cikin gwamnatin tarayya.
