AURORA, Colo. (AP) - Ƙaramin mota ya shiga cikin jama'a, kuma wani yankin Aurora da ke ƙauyen Denver ya yi wa juyayi saboda rashin adalci. An kashe wani yanki a cikin wannan juyayi.
Ƙungiyar Ƙwadago ta Aurora ta ce a kan Twitter cewa 'yan tawaye suna tafiya a Jirgin Ƙasa 225 Alhamis lokacin da wani mota ya shiga ciki.
Sojojin sun ce wani yankin ya rufe wani makami, ya taba ɗan adamu ɗaya ko fiye da haka wanda aka dauka zuwa asibiti cikin yanayi mai kyau.
Gwamnati ta ce motar ta yi towing kuma suna bin diddigin.
Jami'an 'yan sanda sun ce masu yin zanga - zanga sun kuma kashe ƙofar gidan kotu, kuma an fara wuta a ofis.
Gwamnati ta sanar da cewa an yi wani taro ba daidai ba, kuma 'yan sanda suka umurci masu yin taka-tsantsan su fita daga wannan yanki.
Tun da aka aika sakataren ƙasa don yaki da bikin nuna bacin ran a Portland, Oregon, an kara tsananin zafin rikicin da ke faruwa a bikin nuna bacin ran da aka yi a baya game da adalci mai ƙarfi.
Sojojin ƙasa sun yi sanarwa cewa an yi rikici a Seattle a Asabar.
Bikin juyayi da aka fara a ranar 25 ga Mayu, bayan mutuwar George Floyd, wani mutum mai ɗan ƙaramin ƙarfe a Minnesota wanda ya mutu bayan wani ɗan sanda mai ƙaramin ƙarfe ya riƙe shi da ƙafafunsa a kan ƙasa, ya nuna waɗancan yanayi na rashin tsaro da ya haifar da mutuwa.
A Colorado, masu bakin kokari suna kara wa jama'a hankali kan mutuwar Elijah McClain, wanda aka hana shi yayin da yake tafiya a wani titin Aurora a watan Agusta 2019 bayan an kira 911 don sanar da shi a matsayin wanda ya kamata a yi la'akari da shi.
Sojojin sun ɗaura masa ɗaurin ɗan tsaki, kuma likitoci sun ba shi 500 miligiram na ketamin, wani magani mai ɗaukar hankali, don ya yi masa saurin ƙwace hankali.
