Tsohon ruwan Tahoe mai haske da ya fi sani an yi wa shi cunkoso ta saboda canjin yanayi.
South Lake Tahoe, California - A cikin cutar pandemiyar, har ma a ranar aiki, mutane suna ci gaba da ƙara a Pope Beach a Lake Tahoe.
"Na kwana a cikin kwance da tafiya da karɓar mota da kuma yin ɗaukar ruwa a Lake," inji wata yarinya mai suna Dakota.
"Wannan abu mai kyau ne dukkanin mutane suna so su je," in ji Emerica Benitas.
Wannan shi ne dalilin da ya sa aikin tsalle na Matt Meunier yana ci gaba da tafiya mai karfi, har ma a lokacin cutar pandemiyar.
Ya ce ya ga "hankali mai ban mamaki. Lake Tahoe shi ne ruwa mafi tsabta da mafi kyau, ina ganin, a ƙasar nan."
Kuma labarin mara kyau: Lake Tahoe ba shi da tsarki kamar yadda ya kasance lokacin da ya zo nan fiye da shekaru goma sha biyar da suka wuce.
Meunier ya ce, "Abin da muke gani da yawa a yanzu shi ne a kan ƙarfe-ƙarfe."
Ka samu wannan alga mai ban mamaki a kan iyakoki.
Masana sun yi imanin cewa canjin yanayi ya sauya yawan zafin ruwa, kuma hakan ya sauya haske.
Kuma mutane miliyan 15 suke ziyartar wannan tsohon kowace shekara - tare da abin da suke bari bayan su.
Meunier ya ce tafiye - tafiye da yake yin jirgin ruwa don tsabtace ƙasa na tekun ya sami abubuwa masu shekaru.
Meunier ya ce, "Kuma lokacin da na ce cunkushe mai tsohon shekaru, na nufi shekarun '60s da '70s."
Kwalaye na ƙarfe, kwalaye na ƙarfe na ƙwayar soda, kwalaye na ƙarfe na ƙofar kirista daga lokutan da suka gabata.
Masana suna bincika tsawon lokacin da aka ɗaura white disc a cikin Lake Tahoe a kowace shekara , sannan su kuma yi adadin yadda suka ga shi.
Malamin Jami'ar UC Davis Geoff Schladow ya ce wannan "alamar muhimmanci ce game da yadda teku yake lafiya."
Da aka yi ƙiyasin shekara ta baya, tsawon tsawon ɗaukar ruwa ya kai takwas fata.
Wannan ya nuna cewa zaka iya ganin wannan diski a kasa da 80 feet.
Amma, ka yi tunani, kusan shekaru 20 da suka wuce, haske na wannan tsohuwa ya kai tsawon 100 feet.
Wannan shine yanayin da masana ke kokarin gyara.
Amma suna yaki da sauyin yanayin yanayi, ci gaban kusa da teku da kuma abin da aka ƙara wa teku a shekarun 1960: Ɗan tsami mai shigarwa da aka kawo don cin abinci ga kifi.
Ba ya aiki.
Schladow ya ce, "Da shigowar shrimps, babu wani abinci mai kyau a cikin ruwa a nan da nan."
Matsaloli masu dangantaka suna fuskantar tsaunuka da ruwa a duniya.
Abin da muke koyi a nan shi ne, idan ba ka iya aikatawa a Tahoe, to me zai yi wa dukkan ruwa da koguna, ruwa da tsaunuka a ƙasashenmu wadanda ba za su sami matsayin kulawa da ƙarfin ƙarfin da Tahoe ba? Schladow ya ce.
Meunier ya ce yana da "kwarin gwiwa" saboda "idan akwai alamun haske na cutar da muke fuskanta, ina ganin ta nuna cewa al'adu za ta dawo da kanta idan muka saurari wannan matsala, matsalar dan adam, daga gare ta kuma bar ta ta faru. A yanzu haka akwai bayanai."
Ɗaya da Ɗaya sun yi waƙa a wurin ɗaukar ƙwallon ƙafa a California saboda ba su ɗauki masu ɗaukar hankali ba yayin cin abinci (VIDEON) - RT USA News
