Ƙwayar cutar Salmonella ta yi sanadiyyar cutar da 212 mutane a 23 ƙasashe.
CDC da kuma Ma'aikatar Lafiya ta Amurka suna binciken ƙaramar cutar Salmonella da ta yi wa mutane 212 a 23 ƙasashe.
A cikin sanarwar da aka fitar a Juma'a, CDC ta bayyana cewa 87 mutane suna da cutar tun bayan ƙarin bayani da aka fitar a ranar Talata game da cutar.
Agajin ya ce mutane suka fara nuna alamun da suka haɗa da ɗanɗano na salmonella, wanda zai iya ɗaukar watanni biyu zuwa huɗu don nuna alamu tsakanin 19 ga Yuli zuwa 11 ga Yuli.
Tun faruwar ɓarnar, takwas da ɗaya mutane sun shiga asibiti, amma babu rahoton kisan kai.
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta CDC ta ce babu wata gaba ɗaya da aka gano da ke haifar da ɗan salmonella.
