Kanye West ya yi nasiha ga matarsa Kim Kardashian saboda ya bayyana abu mai tsarki a gaban jama'a.
Mawallafi ya bayyana a wani taro a Carolina ta Kudu cewa miji da mata sun yi tunani game da ɓatar da ɗansu na farko.
Bayan mako mai tsanani da ya yi wata shaida a kan matarsa da iyalinta, West ya yi wata sakon nasiha a kan Twitter.
An ruwaito kuma cewa West ya ziyarci asibiti sa'o'i bayan an ziyarce shi da Justin Bieber a gidansa a Wyoming.
Ya ce: "Ina so na yi wa matata Kim nasiha game da yin bayyana da abu da ya shafi al'amari na sirri.
Ba na rufe ta kamar yadda ta rufe ni ba.
Ga Kim ina so in ce na sani na yi maka laifi. Ka yi min afuwa. Na gode da kasancewa tare da ni kullum.
Tweets na West da suka yi waɗannan zargi cewa matarsa ta yi kokarin ɗaukar shi zuwa asibiti da kuma yin zargin da yawa a kan uwar mahaifiyarsa, Kris Jenner.
Ya ce kuma ya yi kokarin yin saki da Kardashian West, wadda ya aure a 2014.
A cikin tsoro game da yanayin zuciyar mijinta, Kardashian West, mahaifiyar yara hudu na West, ta fitar da wata sanarwa mai tsawo cewa ita da iyalinta suna "ba da iko" wajen shiga tsakani, kuma ta tuna masu sauraro da cewa yana da cutar bipolar.
Ta ce: "Shi wani mutum mai kwarewa ne amma mai wahala, wanda a ƙarƙashin ƙarfin zama mawaki da namiji mai launin fata, wanda ya yi fama da raunin kai mai tsanani na uwarsa, kuma ya kamata ya yi magana da ƙarfin da kullewa da aka ƙara ta hanyar cutar bi-polar ɗinsa."
Ta kara da cewa ba ta tattauna yanayinsa ba saboda tana "da matukar kare hakkin yaranmu da kuma hakkin Kanye na sirri game da lafiyarsa."
Ta kara da cewa: "Amma yau, na ji ina da buƙatar in yi magana game da wannan saboda alamun rashin yarda da kuma ƙwayar cutar lafiya."
West ya yi bayaninsa game da sace yaro a wata taro a ranar 19 ga watan Yuli.
Kasuwar cutar Korona ta Isra'ila ta kai 60,000 yayin da cututtuka suka karuwa.
JERUSALEM (Reuters) - Adadin mutane da suka yi kamu da cutar Korona a Isra'ila ya kai 60,000 a Asabar yayin da gwamnatin ta yi kokarin kawar da sake karuwar yawan cutar.
Ƙungiyar lafiya ta ƙasa ta bayyana cewa, an samu ƙarin cutarwa 1,770 a ranar, wanda ya haɗa da yawan cututtuka 60,496.
Da yawan jama'a na miliyan goma, Isra'ila ta rahoto cewa an samu mutuwa 455 daga cutar pandemiya.
Isra'ila ta zama ɗaya daga cikin ƙasashe na farko da suka yi aiki da tsarin kulle kasa baki ɗaya, kuma a farkon haka ta samu nasara wajen ɗaukar matakai don hana yaduwar cutar.
Yawan rahotanni a kowace rana da suka kai ƙimanin dari biyu ya ƙare zuwa ƙananan ƙimar goma sha biyu.
Bayan jin tsoron illa da ta haɗa da tattalin arziki, gwamnatin ta sauya wadannan dokoki - da sauri sosai, kamar yadda wasu ma'aikatan sun bayyana bayanai - kuma yawan cutar ya sake karuwa.
Ƙara sake rufe sassan daban - daban na tattalin arziki ya tsananta damuwar jama'a, haɗa da yin zanga - zangar kullum.
